title: Work With Me
description: I'm available as a research collaborator or for hire as a technical consultant.

body.raw:
I'm available as a consultant via [Everman - Haygood](https://www.evermanhaygood.com), a small consulting firm that I run with my close friend and colleague, Jake Haygood.

We specialize in navigating the technical challenges associated with applying machine learning to real-world problems.

We can provide the most value to someone who has an idea of a new product or service they want to build, but doesn't have the technical expertise to do so. 

<Callout type='warning'>
    You can contact us at [evermanhaygood@gmail.com](mailto:evermanhaygood@gmail.com)
</Callout>

## Contact Me

If you just want to chat, I'm happy to do that as well. Reach out to me!

<Callout type='warning'>
    Find me on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/beneverman) or [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/beneverman/). You can also email me at [evermanben@gmail.com](mailto:evermanben@gmail.com).
</Callout>
